data.description: Must see one owner custom home nestled on a private .98 acre lot in highly rated Midlothian ISD! Saddleback Creek Estates = No HOA! Home offers flexible split floorplan with 3 bedrooms + study or 4 bedrooms* The tall ceilings make the home feel spacious & welcoming - crown molding, recessed lighting & custom fixtures are just a few upgrades you will find.  Kitchen offers beautiful granite counters with breakfast bar, solid wood cabinets & drawers, under counter lighting & stainless steel appliances. Spacious living area with gas start fireplace & surround sound over looks private park like back yard with mature trees. Huge master bedroom with tray ceiling, ensuite bath with oversized shower, dual vanities, linen closet & walk in closet with built-ins - garden tub with beautiful private view. Other upgrades include custom Lafayette shades through out, crown molding, custom storage in mud room, gutters & more! HVAC replaced in 2016, roof 2 yrs old! Come see this amazing home today!
